Tomi Odunsi (amuru 24 Mee 1987) bu onye omere onyonyo nke Naijiria, onye ọbụ abụ na onye na-ede abụ ama ama maka ịkpọ “Salewa” na usoro onyonyo, Tinsel
A mụrụ Tomi Odunsi na 24 May 1987 na Ogun State, Nigeria
Tomi Odunsi gara mahadum Lagos, ebe o nwetara nzere Bachelọ nke Arts (BA) na linguistics na asụsụ Afrịka nwere ọkachamara n'asụsụ Yoruba
Odunsi wepụtara otu mpụta mbụ ya, "I Wan Blow", n'Aprel 2013 wee mee ya na Oriental Hotel n'Ogustu 2013
Odunsi bụ CEO na onye nchoputa nke CGT Media Ltd,  Ntụrụndụ Afrika na mgbasa ozi ụlọ ọrụ.
